profile:
Glaze, don't replace with GlazeMytub!

Thinking of getting a new tub? Why spend extra money and save yourself the extra work when you can just reglaze?

An established business from Toronto, now expanding its services to the eastern provincial region ( such as Ottawa, Gatineau, Clarence-Rockland, Prescott-Russell).

Glazemytub provides exceptional services in:

1. Bathtub glazing
2. Tiles glazing
3. Walk in/shower stall reglazing
4. Shower base reglazing
5. Clawfoot /jacuzzi tub reglazing
6. Sink reglazing
7. Backsplash reglazing
8. Grout cleaning
9. Hardwood cleaning
10. Caulking

We also specialize in chip and crack repair.

We use environmentally friendly, durable and high quality products.

Insured (WSIB)
Warranty provided for 3 years

High ratings of customer satisfaction

Contact 647 620 2341 for a quote!
